Quickstrike:





Quickstrike grinned he was saluted, then perked up himself as he 
heard the rumble. He saw the three bots run into the corridor. He 
jumped down from the command chair, and stepped forward, wondering 
what the sound was. An attack was his guess.

He was getting a little nervous about this. He opened his comm-link 
to Venomous. "See anyone outside?"
